    "When fine-tuning and evaluating on Chest X-ray14 [33], CheXpert [6], and RSNA Pneumonia [34], C2L outperforms supervised models pretrained on ImageNet and self-supervised models pretrained with MoCo [24].",
    "Other variants of MoCo have also exhibited improvement over fully supervised learning for CXR classification [35][36][37][38].",
